      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a collector-grade example of the legendary S54-powered platform. The high-revving 3.2L inline-six features individual throttle bodies and delivers linear power up to its 8,000 RPM redline. Power is managed through a precise Getrag six-speed manual gearbox and a limited-slip M Differential. This vehicle features documented subframe reinforcement and a full VANOS overhaul, ensuring mechanical longevity. The chassis remains exceptionally rigid with no bushing deflection, and the original paint retains its factory luster. A truly turn-key, investment-quality machine for the discerning driver.",
